1. Create new folder `packages/<provider>`
2. Set version in `packages/<provider>/package.json` to `0.0.0`
3. Create changeset for new package with `major` version bump
4. Add examples to `examples/ai-functions/src/*/<provider>.ts` (based on supported model types)
5. Add documentation in `content/providers/01-ai-sdk-providers/<number>-<provider>.mdx`
6. Reference PR example: https://github.com/vercel/ai/pull/8136/files

---

### 12. Source File Structure Examples

**Luma (Image Provider):**
- `src/index.ts` - Main export
- `src/luma-provider.ts` - Provider initialization
- `src/luma-image-model.ts` - Image model implementation
- `src/luma-image-settings.ts` - Model ID types & settings
- `src/luma-image-model.test.ts` - Tests
