- `src/fal-transcription-model.ts` - Transcription implementation
- `src/fal-config.ts` - Common configuration
- `src/fal-error.ts` - Error handling
- `src/version.ts` - Version constant

**OpenAI (Complex Provider):**
- Organized in subdirectories: `chat/`, `completion/`, `embedding/`, `speech/`, `transcription/`, `responses/`, `internal/`
- Internal export for advanced features

---

### 13. Key Dependencies

**All providers depend on:**
- `@ai-sdk/provider` (workspace:*) - Core provider interfaces
- `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` (workspace:*) - Utilities (loadApiKey, withUserAgentSuffix, etc.)
- `zod` - Schema validation (peerDependency: ^3.25.76 || ^4.1.8)

**DevDependencies:**
- `@ai-sdk/test-server` - Test utilities
- `@vercel/ai-tsconfig` - Shared TypeScript config
- `tsup` ^8 - Build tool
- `typescript` 5.8.3

---

### 14. Files Structure Summary

```
packages/<provider>/
├── src/
│   ├── index.ts                           # Main exports
│   ├── <provider>-provider.ts             # Provider factory
│   ├── <provider>-<model-type>-model.ts   # Model implementations
│   ├── <provider>-<model-type>-settings.ts # Model ID types
│   ├── <provider>-error.ts                 # Error handling
│   ├── <provider>-error.test.ts           # Error tests
│   ├── <provider>-provider.test.ts        # Provider tests
│   ├── version.ts                         # VERSION constant
